column5: I was wondering if anyone knows how many amps the alternator puts out on a 75 hp 4 stroke Merc when cruising?
When you check the Merc (Black Anchor) site, they should give it under the motor specs.  See here: http://www.mercurymarine.com/engines/outbo...specs.php?ID=77
depending on the year, 20 to 50 amps
